in.teramatrix.flint.driver.fragment

Class HomeFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v4.app.Fragment
      • in.teramatrix.flint.driver.fragment.HomeFragment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener

    public class HomeFragment
extends android.support.v4.app.Fragment
    It is the main dashboard of the application consists of three different fragment in a CustomViewPager in this version. Fragments are as following...
    • TicketListFragment
      • For Closed tickets
    • TicketListFragment
      • For Opened tickets
    • NotificationFragment
      • For Notifications
    There will not be any UI thread issue in this fragment because data is loaded in each fragment separately.
    Author:
    Mohsin Khan
    Date:
    14/9/2016
